## Configuration

On first launch, go to **Settings tab** to:
1. Select **OpenAI** or **Ollama** provider
2. Enter your **API key** (for OpenAI) or set **Ollama URL** (default: localhost:11434)
3. Choose your preferred model
4. Manage custom prompt templates

